\
The three CORAL labs developed a single request for Proposal(RFP) that specified the requirements and desired features of a system to meet the needs of Department of Energy\'92s Office of Science and National Nuclear Security Administration. One requirement was that the ORNL and ANL would have computers with different architectures to manage risk. 
